cross: Cymbidium Red Beauty x Cymbidium Kirbey Lesh

measurements.description: Eleven flowers on one upright inflorescence; sepals and petals slightly cupped, cream, striped and overlaid pink-rose; lip cream, side lobes speckled pink rose upper edge, midlobe spotted and edged maroon, keels yellow, speckled maroon; column dark maroon, anther cap cream, lightly speckled maroon; substance firm; texture matte.
